description: Never add AI co-author trailers to git commits
alwaysApply: true
---

# Git Commit Authorship

- Never add `Co-authored-by`, `Signed-off-by`, or any other trailer attributing Cursor, Composer, Claude, or any AI agent to commits.
- Commit messages must contain only the user's authorship.
- Do not append attribution footers to commit messages under any circumstance.
